{"tid":1897384,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"公民黨因爲怕失去立法會法律界功能組別席位，所以由第一個火魔開始，已私下同抗爭者割席","createTime":"2020-02-25T16:43:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T05:57:03.000Z","uid":230104,"like":16,"dislike":52,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"a790cedfe532ebbe97a11a3c972c29913454a067","tid":1897384,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T16:43:26.000Z","msg":"歷史回顧， 當時網民一吹雞，公民黨Body楊、黨賓周梁家傑都喺地鐵現場出現，幫手足解圍<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7ohQAy9db4s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7ohQAy9db4s&d=JcMWRxryG4qpJesfomKpWJktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=070a88ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7ohQAy9db4s</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/BFtDFxcnT-Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBFtDFxcnT-Y&d=JcMWRxryG4qpJesfomKpWJktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=5b1b92e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/BFtDFxcnT-Y</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而自從第一個火魔出現後，公民黨就生怕藍絲法律界既指責，從而令佢地立律界功能組別不保，<br />\n<br />\n自始之後，得返唔係律師既譚文豪對抗黑警，<br />\n<br />\n其餘律師黨友，再無出現喺街頭幫手足出頭，集體失蹤，導致過千手足被非法濫捕，叫天不應叫地不聞<br />\n<br />\n呢場運動無需大台，由市民主導，<br />\n<br />\n但不代表義士在現場受不合理不合法濫捕時，最懂法律既「自己友」消失得無影無蹤<br />\n<br />\n唯一見到佢地既時候，係區議會選舉拉票時<br />\n<br />\n公民黨，市民可以送你們區議員上台，也可以在立法會選舉，要你地讓位給真正幫手足既人上台<br />\n<br />\n最後，希望你們回頭是岸"},{"pid":"3fecf693f6c40f4e670aa5cf6b2cf2fde63a08d5","tid":1897384,"uid":173849,"like":19,"dislike":10,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T16:48:31.000Z","msg":"選舉近了，保皇狗開始抹黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBlocked"},{"pid":"6b1786402c0f5168f769863983e26b4dc9205e2d","tid":1897384,"uid":111616,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T16:53:27.000Z","msg"